[32m│[0m ## Security Testing Implications                                             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### **Critical Vulnerabilities Identified**                                  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m #### 1. **XXE (XML External Entity) Injection** [HIGH RISK]                  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Why vulnerable**: No schema validation allows DOCTYPE declarations         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ```xml                                                                       [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m <?xml version="1.0"?>                                                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m <!DOCTYPE foo [                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m   <!ENTITY xxe SYSTEM "file:///etc/passwd">                                  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ]>                                                                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m <book><title>&xxe;</title></book>                                            [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ```                                                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Potential Impact**: File disclosure, SSRF, DoS                             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m #### 2. **XML Bomb / Billion Laughs** [HIGH RISK]                            [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Why vulnerable**: No entity expansion limits configured                    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ```xml                                                                       [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m <?xml version="1.0"?>                                                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m <!DOCTYPE lolz [                                                             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m   <!ENTITY lol "lol">                                                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m   <!ENTITY lol2 "&lol;&lol;&lol;&lol;">                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m   <!-- Exponential expansion -->                                             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ]>                                                                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m <book><title>&lol2;</title></book>                                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ```                                                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Potential Impact**: Denial of Service                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m #### 3. **XPath Injection** [MEDIUM RISK]                                    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Why vulnerable**: Unvalidated XML structure processed                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Potential Impact**: Data manipulation, unauthorized access                 [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m #### 4. **Data Integrity Compromise** [MEDIUM RISK]                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Why vulnerable**: No format validation on business-critical fields         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Potential Impact**: Database pollution, invalid catalog data               [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
